show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/RG3ar3
show.description: A physically challenged guy, heir to billions, has the soul of Earth's most powerful god reborn within him, making him a god on Earth. After his dad suddenly dies, everyone's eyes are on his property. So, deadly attacks start on him, aiming to kill him and seize his dad's wealth. Three powerful goddesses are protecting him. How will he protect his dad's property and himself from his enemies? Can those three goddesses save him from his foes?
